Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:17.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上的羽翼 已经与你一同消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:26.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞翔时的记忆 却无法像擦伤一样消去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:37.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你寻回 是我一直所想之事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:45.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你不随时间的浊流 被浪冲走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:53.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法说出些许回忆 始终无依无靠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:01:01.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残留下的些许眼泪 却一定无法传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:07.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的泪滴 也将坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.97,0:01:16.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间黑夜被撕裂 光芒飞散于空中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:23.85,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洁净如洗的太阳 温柔地照耀着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:29.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱着你一起前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:40.73,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,描绘出的梦之画卷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:49.16,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去轻轻触摸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.74,0:22:55.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伸出的指尖 它淡淡消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.19,0:23:02.93,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 真实的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:12.83,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧 聆听这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:21.85,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份满溢的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:31.98,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定能传达给最重视的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:13.57,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}欢迎 欢迎来到卡扎姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:21.57,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}我们尊贵的真王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:37.42,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}王兽们也振翅欢迎真王陛下驾临
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:45.55,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}我们在圣洁的光辉中迎来陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粪便清理完了后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就开始铺稻草
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要整理得和自己的床铺一样干净哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没在看什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真王陛下的来访能安安稳稳的渡过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经很安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果你指挥王兽在空中飞翔一事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被真王陛下知晓的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜她会怎么想?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇里库老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嘴风很紧的 你无需担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:25.70,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,250)}{\fad(1000,0)}{\blur3}斗蛇的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真王陛下是乘船回去的是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沿着卡扎姆附近的河流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘着座船只回王都去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们也能在瞭望台上看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利沙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窥视真王陛下的乘船是很失礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾沙鲁老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想带学童们去观察大自然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观察大自然?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像艾琳老师常常做的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让学童们了解下书本上说的花草和动物的真实模样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能只让学童们学习王兽的知识呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观察大自然可是不错的主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过可不能放任过头 要是从瞭望台上滑下去可就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究只是个自然观察课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意让学童们用心观察
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚了没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许我们去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下能看到真王的船了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧去准备下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郊游去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏南大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是目前斗蛇军的报告书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 我等下会看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁甘大人回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁甘他…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏南…苏南…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真王领民…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍隆们根本就不会懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们保护着众神之子圣洁的真王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我们让国家富强昌盛的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 这话我可不能充耳不闻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您忘记了对真王陛下的忠义之心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁甘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为父亲有事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过得我尽快赶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场上的士兵还在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想说这事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能尽量缩短战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真王陛下离开王宫一事你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果此时让斗蛇军太过活跃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会招致真王领民们的胡乱猜忌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此 我们才能击退拉扎军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些猜忌就不攻自破了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血秽们的活动日益频繁想必你也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家出现的扭曲已经到了无法挽回的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家族代代都是不惜玷污自己的身躯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来保护真王陛下维护这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后这一势力也不会有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此尽心尽责 我们尽到忠诚就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都认为你是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该是强大有力并和蔼可亲地为我指引道路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不得不这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今已容不得我停留片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达弥亚 我至今从未如此亲近过我的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是有小王兽诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不曾想过要离开王宫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了这次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会能出来看看人们的真实生活模样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下就是指引人们前进 无可替代的明灯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为真王所存在的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是能为人民所造福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就继续下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管去的时候不得翻山越岭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来时可以先在卡扎姆的旅馆歇息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后沿着河岸返回不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到真王陛下的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘船的话会轻松不少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆乘的船差不多该回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 在这个季节里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡扎姆河的风景一定更加迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想等她回来听她说说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:11:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 大家一人一个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还真是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真王陛下的船还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是座船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像整个城堡都在船上一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没见过这种船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壮观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一趟来得还真值啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西珑 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西从支流那边飘过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有斗蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们冲着屋型船过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有斗蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击队 上弓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是斗蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大公的人攻击过来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们不能让它们靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达弥亚大人 请您先保护好陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊亚尔 要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真王陛下被斗蛇…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方的帆船被击沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:14:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳 你要去做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔 斗蛇从后面上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要当心背后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰 让我坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真王陛下在被斗蛇攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点去救她的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 我不会让你飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你和比兰一现身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要利用你的人就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护背负大罪而死去的索永之愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望王兽被人类的规矩所束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能眼睁睁的见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋大公 竟想用斗蛇暗杀真王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:17:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,载着人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在飞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让你破坏我们的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰 再飞去那里一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰用它那锋利的爪子和尖锐的牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将斗蛇撕裂 咬碎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇的粘液夹杂着麝香的甘甜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血腥之味空中弥散
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被激发出野性的王兽压倒性的攻击着斗蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类只能无言的看着这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 比兰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达弥亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下昏倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是遥远的太古时代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自亚芬诺亚山脉另一边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降临在塔海亚泽的神圣的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使成千上万的斗蛇也一举歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是王的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 操控它的圣洁少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是何等绝妙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是由自己引起的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被眼前的事实所击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳惊呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能眼睁睁的望着这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.92,0:24:05.49,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回王宫的船受到了斗蛇的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:08.10,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不省人事的真王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.16,0:24:10.59,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被送到了卡扎姆的官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.33,0:24:13.10,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在压倒性的力量面前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.23,0:24:15.64,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚盾只是把无力的破盾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.43,0:24:18.72,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连该守护的东西都守护不了的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:20.70,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么生存下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.59,0:24:22.97,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兽之奏者 艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.39,0:24:24.70,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌云笼罩的国家
